Ted Levine https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ted_Levine 0 Frank Theodore Levine (born May 29, 1957) is an American actor. He is known for his roles as Buffalo Bill in The Silence of the Lambs and as Captain Leland Stottlemeyer in the television series Monk.
